{
  "sn11.21:0.1": "Saṃyutta Nikāya 11 ",
  "sn11.21:0.2": "3. Tatiyavagga ",
  "sn11.21:0.3": "21. Chetvāsutta ",
  "sn11.21:1.1": "Sāvatthiyaṃ jetavane. ",
  "sn11.21:1.2": "Atha kho sakko devānamindo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. ",
  "sn11.21:1.3": "Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho sakko devānamindo bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: ",
  "sn11.21:2.1": "“Kiṃsu chetvā sukhaṃ seti, ",
  "sn11.21:2.2": "kiṃsu chetvā na socati; ",
  "sn11.21:2.3": "Kissassu ekadhammassa, ",
  "sn11.21:2.4": "vadhaṃ rocesi gotamā”ti. ",
  "sn11.21:3.1": "“Kodhaṃ chetvā sukhaṃ seti, ",
  "sn11.21:3.2": "kodhaṃ chetvā na socati; ",
  "sn11.21:3.3": "Kodhassa visamūlassa, ",
  "sn11.21:3.4": "madhuraggassa vāsava; ",
  "sn11.21:3.5": "Vadhaṃ ariyā pasaṃsanti, ",
  "sn11.21:3.6": "tañhi chetvā na socatī”ti. "
}